#: ../../docs/technical/use-cases.rst:13
msgid ""
"Products have varying attributes like color, size, material that don't "
"warrant dedicated columns. HStore stores them as flat key-value pairs with a"
" clean admin interface."
msgstr ""
"Products में color, size, material जैसे विविध attributes होते हैं जिनके लिए "
"dedicated columns की आवश्यकता नहीं होती। HStore इन्हें clean admin interface"
" के साथ flat key-value pairs के रूप में store करता है।"

